lading report attached. It gave only fifteen days of half-life remaining. Not very much, he reflected.

55
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:22,000
Automatically he pressed a portable photo-phazon amplifier into the transparent plastic hull

56
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:27,760
of the casket, tuned it, listened at the proper frequency for indication of cephalic activity.

57
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:30,800
Faintly, from the speaker, a voice said,

58
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:38,080
And then Tillie sprained her ankle, and we never thought it'd heal. She was so foolish about it,

59
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:44,720
wanted to start walking immediately. Satisfied, he unplugged the amplifier and located the union

60
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:51,200
man to perform the actual task of carting 3054039B to the consultation lounge,

61
00:05:51,760 --> 00:05:54,640
where the customer would be put in touch with the old lady.

62
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:59,840
You checked her out, did you? The customer asked as he paid the post-grad's due.

63
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:06,080
Personally, Herbert answered, functioning perfectly. He kicked a series of switches,

64
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:10,080
