00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:16,080
not indicated, not by any means. Where's Ella? He halted, glanced rapidly about.

117
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:22,320
I bring her from the bin to the consultation lounge for you, Herbert said. Customers should

118
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:27,280
