322
00:31:24,080 --> 00:31:29,680
Glancing at Runceter, he said, Jory passed at fifteen. That's why he has so much vitality.

323
00:31:30,320 --> 00:31:35,120
Actually, this has happened before. Jory has shown up several times where he shouldn't be.

324
00:31:36,080 --> 00:31:42,800
Once more into the microphone, he said, This is very unfair of you, Jory. Mr. Runceter has come

325
00:31:42,800 --> 00:31:47,920
