328
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:04,480
What did he say? Runceter demanded. Will he get out of there and let me talk to Ella?

329
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:12,480
Von Vogel Sang said, There's nothing Jory can do. Think of two AM radio transmitters,

330
00:32:12,480 --> 00:32:19,120
one close by but limited to only five hundred watts of operating power, then another far off,

331
00:32:19,120 --> 00:32:24,240
but on the same or nearly the same frequency and utilizing five thousand watts.

332
00:32:25,360 --> 00:32:34,000
When night comes and night, Runceter said, has come, at least for Ella, and maybe himself as well,

333
00:32:34,560 --> 00:32:40,400
if Hollis' missing teeps, paracinetists, precogs, resurrectors, and animators couldn't be found.

334
00:32:41,200 --> 00:32:48,160
He had not only lost Ella, he had also lost her advice, Jory having supplanted her before she could

335
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:54,960
give it. When we return her to the bin, Von Vogel Sang was blabbing, we won't install her near Jory

