00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:08,160
in a high-grade isolated chamber with walls coated and reinforced with Teflon 26 so as to

338
00:33:08,160 --> 00:33:15,200
inhibit hetero-psychic infusion from Jory or anybody else. Isn't it too late?

339
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:19,920
Runceter said, surfacing momentarily from the depression into which this happening had dropped

340
00:33:19,920 --> 00:33:28,160
him. She may return. Once Jory phases out, plus anyone else who may have gotten into her because

341
00:33:28,160 --> 00:33:34,320
of her weak in state, she's accessible to almost anyone. Von Vogel Sang chewed his lip palpably

342
00:33:34,320 --> 00:33:42,720
pondering. She may not like being isolated, Mr. Runceter. We keep the containers, the caskets,

343
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:47,680
as they're called by the lay public, close together for a reason, wandering through one

344
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:54,240
another's mind, gives those in half-life the only, put her in solitary right now, Runceter broke in.

345
00:33:54,240 --> 00:34:00,400
Better she be isolated than not exist at all. She exists, Von Vogel Sang corrected.

346
00:34:00,400 --> 00:34:04,960
She merely can't contact you. There's a difference. Runceter said,

347
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:07,680
a metaphysical difference which means nothing to me.

348
00:34:08,240 --> 00:34:14,880
I will put her in isolation, Von Vogel Sang said, but I think you're right. It's too late.

349
00:34:15,680 --> 00:34:24,560
Jory has permeated her permanently to some extent, at least I'm sorry. Runceter said harshly, so am I.

350
00:34:28,080 --> 00:34:28,400
3.

351
00:34:30,560 --> 00:34:35,280
Instant, you, Bick, has all the fresh flavor of just-brewed drip coffee. Your husband will say,

352
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:42,320
Christ, Sally, I used to think your coffee was only so-so, but now, wow! safe when taken as directed.

