dime and with it started up the coffee pot. Sniffing the, to him very unusual smell, he again

448
00:44:14,480 --> 00:44:19,200
consulted his watch, saw that fifteen minutes had passed. He therefore vigorously strode to the

449
00:44:19,200 --> 00:44:25,680
apt door, turned the knob and pulled on the release bolt. The door refused to open. It said,

450
00:44:26,560 --> 00:44:31,120
Five cents, please. He searched his pockets. No more coins, nothing.

451
00:44:31,760 --> 00:44:36,240
I'll pay you tomorrow, he told the door. Again he tried the knob. Again it remained locked tight.

452
