What I pay you, he informed it, is in the nature of a gratuity. I don't have to pay you.

453
00:44:42,560 --> 00:44:47,680
I think otherwise, the door said. Look in the purchase contract you signed when you bought this

454
00:44:47,680 --> 00:44:53,200
