471
00:46:36,080 --> 00:46:39,600
Caveat emtor, it read. He wondered what that meant.

472
00:46:40,320 --> 00:46:46,400
This is Pat, G.G. Ashwood said, his arm with ostentatious familiarity around the girl's waist.

473
00:46:46,400 --> 00:46:52,880
Never mind her last name. Square and puffy like an overweight brick, wearing his usual mohair poncho,

474
00:46:52,880 --> 00:46:58,400
apricot-colored felt hat, argile ski socks, and carpet slippers. He advanced toward Joe Chip,

475
00:46:58,400 --> 00:47:05,440
self-satisfaction smirking from every molecule in his body. He had found something of value here,

476
00:47:05,440 --> 00:47:10,640
and he meant to make the most of it. Pat, this is the company's highly skilled first-line electrical

477
00:47:10,640 --> 00:47:14,320
type tester. Coolly the girl said to Joe Chip,

478
00:47:15,120 --> 00:47:23,520
is it you that's electrical or your tests? We trade off, Joe said. He felt from all around

479
00:47:23,680 --> 00:47:29,280
him the miasma of his uncleaned-up apt. It radiated the specter of debris and clutter,

480
00:47:29,280 --> 00:47:31,280
and he knew that Pat had already noticed.

481
00:47:32,400 --> 00:47:35,680
Sit down, he said awkwardly. Have a cup of actual coffee.

482
00:47:36,560 --> 00:47:41,760
Such luxury, Pat said, seating herself at the kitchen table. Reflexively,

483
00:47:41,760 --> 00:47:44,800
she gathered the week's heap of papes into a neater pile.

484
00:47:45,760 --> 00:47:48,240
How can you afford real coffee, Mr. Chip?

485
00:47:49,200 --> 00:47:53,840
G.G. Ashwood said, Joe gets paid a hell of a lot. The firm could not break without him.

486
00:47:54,560 --> 00:47:57,760
Reaching out, he took a cigarette from the package lying on the table.

487
00:47:57,760 --> 00:48:04,080
Put it back, Joe Chip said. I'm almost out, and I used up my last green ration stamp on the coffee.

488
00:48:04,640 --> 00:48:10,400
I paid for the door, G.G. pointed out. He offered the pack to the girl. Joe puts on an act,

489
00:48:10,400 --> 00:48:16,320
