490
00:48:16,320 --> 00:48:18,560
Where's your test equipment, Joe? We're wasting time.

491
00:48:19,600 --> 00:48:23,120
To the girl, Joe said, you're dressed oddly.

492
00:48:24,080 --> 00:48:30,000
I maintained the subsurface vid phone lines at the Topeka Kibbutz, Pat said. Only women can hold

493
00:48:30,000 --> 00:48:34,880
jobs involving manual labor at that particular Kibbutz. That's why I applied there instead of

494
00:48:34,880 --> 00:48:43,680
the Wichita Falls Kibbutz. Her black eyes blazed pridefully. Joe said, that inscription on your arm,

495
00:48:44,320 --> 00:48:51,280
tattoo, is that Hebrew? Latin. Her eyes veiled her amusement. I've never seen an app so cluttered

496
00:48:51,280 --> 00:48:56,480
with rubbish. Don't you have a mistress? These electrical expert types have no time for

497
