530
00:52:08,320 --> 00:52:13,920
Let me explain, Joe said, how the anti-precog generally functions— functions, in fact,

531
00:52:13,920 --> 00:52:20,160
in every case we know of. The precog sees a variety of futures laid outside by side,

532
00:52:20,160 --> 00:52:26,480
like cells in a beehive. For him, one has greater luminosity unless he picks.

533
00:52:27,200 --> 00:52:32,400
Once he has picked it, the anti-precog can do nothing. The anti-precog has to be present

534
00:52:32,400 --> 00:52:39,200
when the precog is in the process of deciding, not after. The anti-precog makes all futures seem

535
00:52:39,200 --> 00:52:46,880
