537
00:52:52,400 --> 00:52:54,960
In the case of telepaths, a similar impairment—

538
00:52:54,960 --> 00:53:00,400
She goes back in time, G. G. Ashwood said. Joe stared at him.

539
00:53:01,200 --> 00:53:08,800
Back in time, G. G. repeated, savoring this. His eyes shot shafts of significance to every

