541
00:53:14,640 --> 00:53:20,160
like you said, the one luminous possibility, and he chooses it, and he's right. But why is it right?

542
00:53:20,800 --> 00:53:25,120
Why is it luminous? Because this girl, he shrugged in her direction,

543
00:53:25,120 --> 00:53:30,720
path controls the future. That one luminous possibility is luminous because she's gone

544
00:53:30,720 --> 00:53:36,000
