he decided, I'm not ready to make my formal report to this society. I'll have to vid Niggleman and

4712
06:19:30,880 --> 06:19:36,000
ask for a postponement. Using a payphone, he called Niggleman back in the North American

4713
06:19:36,000 --> 06:19:42,720
Confederation. Len, he said, I can't do any more today. I've spent the last twelve hours trying

4714
06:19:42,720 --> 06:19:47,280
